RSI Howling Moon’s Hard Shell Roof Top Tent

Strong & durable, sleek fibreglass shell top & bottom. New scratch resistant coating over the fibreglass. Gas strut lifting mechanism makes opening effortless. The fully quilted comfort high density 100mm foam mattress gives you a home from home nights’ rest!

 

Specs:
• Weight 75kg
• Outer dimensions (closed) L220xW150xH33cm
• Inside dimensions (open) L215xW145xH105cm

 

Click here to view the entire range of RSI SmartCap Evo Canopies available!

Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!

 

Please note: Depending on stock & availability, the current wait time for this product is approx. 30 – 90 days from date of order.
